#: ../../draft/intro/use_cases.rst:8
msgid "Use cases"
msgstr "应用场景"

#: ../../draft/intro/use_cases.rst:10
msgid "*IT as a Service*"
msgstr "*IT即服务*"

#: ../../draft/intro/use_cases.rst:12
msgid ""
"An IT organization wants to control applications, available to cloud users. "
"Application management should be simple and not time-consuming. Users should"
" be able to easily find and create the desired applications."
msgstr ""
"一个IT组织打算控制应用程序，提供给云的用户。应用的管理须足够简单且不能花费太多"
"时间，用户还可轻松的发现和创建想要的应用。"

#: ../../draft/intro/use_cases.rst:16
msgid "*Self-service portal*"
msgstr "*自服务门户*"

#: ../../draft/intro/use_cases.rst:18
msgid ""
"You may want to create compound combinations of applications dynamically "
"from simple app blocks. And you can create an environment that satisfies "
"your requirements in a matter of minutes. Examples of such an environment "
"may be “Jenkins+Java+Tomcat” or “Jenkins+Gerrit+Java+JBoss”. So testing "
"application in different environment combinations becomes easier."
msgstr ""
"你或许打算从几个简单的app来动态的创建混合的应用程序。又或者是你在短短的几分"
"钟内就可以创建出满意的环境，例如“Jenkins+Java+Tomcat” 或 “Jenkins+Gerrit+Java+JBoss”"
"的环境。那么Murano让这些测试的应用在不同的环境变得更加简单。"

#: ../../draft/intro/use_cases.rst:24
msgid "*Glue layer use case*"
msgstr "粘合层用例"

#: ../../draft/intro/use_cases.rst:26
msgid ""
"Any external service or technology may be linked to the application in the "
"cloud. It can be done using the powerful Murano architecture. For example, "
"Murano supports Docker and OracleDB applications, and to enable this support"
" no single change was made to Murano itself. So, users can integrate with "
"new external services with a minimum cost. Currently, murano applications "
"have been integrated with the following technologies: Docker, Legacy apps "
"VMs or bare metal, apps outside of OpenStack, and the following ones are "
"planned for the future: cloudify and TOSCA, apache brooklin, APS."
msgstr ""
"在云的内部的一些应用或许和外部的服务或技术有联系，这可以通过强大的Murano架构"
"来完成。举例来说，Murano支持Docker和OracleDB的应用，且启动这些支持，仅Murano"
"本身就可独立完成。所以，用户以最小的代价整合了外部的服务。目前，Murano应用已经"
"整合的技术有：Docker,旧的应用虚拟机或物理机，OpenStack之外的app,而且，即将整合"
"的有：cloudify和 TOSCA，apache brooklin,APS等。"
